<item>
            <title>[LU-11189] OSC flow control</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11189</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re running into a problem that somehow OST devices are really slow to serve write requests. However, clients don&apos;t the situation so they would just keep sending requests, eventually this causes RPC timeout.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This work is trying to relieve the problem by introducing a flow control on the OSC where it holds sending more requests as soon as it receives early reply.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
